SourceString:
Full face cover gasmask fitted with Night-Vision Goggles, covered in arcane runes. 

Looks like the sort of thing worn by Cultists. It also completely obscures the face...
Press :HelmLight: to toggle on and off your Night Vision.
LocalizedString: Нажмите :HelmLight:, чтобы включить или выключить ПНВ.
